Package: dplyrExtras
Type: Package
Title: extra functionality for dplyr like mutate_if
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-05-25
Author: Sebastian Kranz
Maintainer: Sebastian Kranz <sebastian.kranz@uni-ulm.de>
Description: Some extra functionality that is not (yet) in dplyr, e.g. mutate_if or s_filter, s_arrange ,... that allow string arguments.
License: GPL>=2.0
Depends: dplyr, data.table
